{"tid":1186962,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講低你公司入面個個小人","createTime":"2019-06-05T09:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T09:55:03.000Z","uid":129269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f72057b8d3e99fffd874278692bfd3cc76dc5c0","tid":1186962,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"翻緊實習<br />\n本身都對個小人無咩特別感覺<br />\n慢慢越黎越唔鍾意佢<br />\n係老細前後兩個人<br />\n對住老細扮乖仔<br />\n係咁問問題博表現 奶哂鞋底<br />\n其他人問老細問題就係隔離加嘴懶叻: &ldquo;下，xxxx咪得囉。&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無諗過當時人會比你害到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係係老細面前落自己同事面博表現囉<br />\n你成日問埋d濕9問題我地都無駁嘴啦<br />\n都唔知你係唔識soft skills定真係奶鞋底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家屌9職場小人"},{"pid":"e63d57621de8b0a2e70e625db24ce09fee8a0ace","tid":1186962,"uid":177448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"佢已經辭咗職半年<br />\n但係keep住mon實我公司個facebook page<br />\n一有update就whatsapp我話乜乜柒柒<br />\n仲成日問公司呢排有乜嘢八掛 eg:兩個上司依家關係點點點 啲客又點點點<br />\n有次仲問我拎公司啲資源畀佢啲friend實習用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f587d169364d40f27bba8ea85de313260fe6cb","tid":1186962,"uid":129269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e63d57621de8b0a2e70e625db24ce09fee8a0ace","tid":1186962,"uid":177448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"佢已經辭咗職半年<br />\n但係keep住mon實我公司個facebook page<br />\n一有update就whatsapp我話乜乜柒柒<br />\n仲成日問公司呢排有乜嘢八掛 eg:兩個上司依家關係點點點 啲客又點點點<br />\n有次仲問我拎公司啲資源畀佢啲friend實習用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢條友都幾多事"}]}